		<tr>
			<td>Physical indicators
			<td> &#8226 aggregate stability
				<br> &#8226 available water capacity
				<br> &#8226 bulk density
				<br> &#8226 infiltration
				<br> &#8226 slaking
				<br> &#8226 soil crusts
				<br> &#8226 soil structures and macropores
			<td>Percolation rate, infiltration rate, water holding capacity, drainage, tillage, aeration, texture and structure of soil
		<tr>
			<td>Biological indicators
